BIB                 11         23
TITLE      An improved internal Cu3-As-alloy cyclotron target for
            the production of 75Br and 77Br and separation of the
            by-product 67Ga from the matrix activity
AUTHOR     (G.Blessing, S.M.Qaim)
INSTITUTE  (2GERJUL)
REFERENCE  (J,ARI,35,927,1984)
FACILITY   (ISOCY,2GERJUL) CV28 compact cyclotron
SAMPLE     Cu3-As alloy (with composition of As (31%) and Cu
            (69%) layer (about 10 micro-meter thick) on a wedged
            copper-backing.
METHOD     (INTB,SITA,ACTIV)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information on the source of uncertainty
COMMENT    *Comment by authors
           The major radionucledic impurity in 75Br is 76Br (5-8%
            at EOB). Batch yields amount to 200mCi 75Br (at EOB)
            and 48 mCi 77Br (at EOB)
STATUS     (TABLE,,G.Blessing+,J,ARI,35,927,1984) Text (p.929)
